    "We will implement three fundamental image operations:\n",
    "\n",
    "1. **Brightness Adjustment**: Adding a constant to all pixel values\n",
    "2. **Contrast Enhancement**: Scaling pixel values around the mean\n",
    "3. **Grayscale Conversion**: Weighted combination of color channels\n",
    "\n",
    "Each operation demonstrates key array manipulation concepts."
