    "**Analysis:**\n",
    "- **Standard deviation** measures contrast (spread of pixel values)\n",
    "- Higher $\alpha$ ‚Üí Higher std ‚Üí More contrast\n",
    "- Lower $\alpha$ ‚Üí Lower std ‚Üí Less contrast (more gray)"
