    "## 5. Results\n",
    "\n",
    "### Summary of Operations\n",
    "\n",
    "| Operation | Mathematical Formula | Effect | Key Concept |\n",
    "|-----------|---------------------|---------|-------------|\n",
    "| Brightness | $I + \\Delta b$ | Shifts all values | Broadcasting with scalar |\n",
    "| Contrast | $(I - \\mu) \\times \\alpha + \\mu$ | Scales around mean | Element-wise arithmetic |\n",
    "| Grayscale | $\\sum w_i \\times C_i$ | Combines channels | Dot product with weights |\n",
    "\n",
    "### Performance Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "All operations are **O(n)** where n = number of pixels, thanks to NumPy's vectorization."
   ]
